<section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-accent-50 animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-alexandria mb-4">
          FAQ
        </span>
        
        <h2 class="font-alexandria font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm bloom-card">
          <button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFAQ('faq-1')">
            <span class="font-alexandria font-medium text-primary-800">Can I pay in parts?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" id="faq-1-arrow">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div id="faq-1" class="hidden px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-primary-700">
              Yes! Both packages offer flexible payment options. You can pay the full amount upfront or choose our payment plan with a smaller initial payment followed by monthly installments.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm bloom-card">
          <button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFAQ('faq-2')">
            <span class="font-alexandria font-medium text-primary-800">How long does it take to build a website?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" id="faq-2-arrow">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div id="faq-2" class="hidden px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-primary-700">
              Simple websites typically take 2-3 weeks, while enhanced websites take 4-6 weeks. This includes design, development, revisions, and testing. I'll provide a detailed timeline during our initial consultation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm bloom-card">
          <button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFAQ('faq-3')">
            <span class="font-alexandria font-medium text-primary-800">What's included in the 5 months of free support?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" id="faq-3-arrow">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div id="faq-3" class="hidden px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-primary-700">
              Free support includes bug fixes, minor content updates, technical assistance, and guidance on using your website. It doesn't include major design changes or new features, but I'm always happy to discuss additional work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm bloom-card">
          <button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFAQ('faq-4')">
            <span class="font-alexandria font-medium text-primary-800">Do you provide hosting and domain services?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" id="faq-4-arrow">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div id="faq-4" class="hidden px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-primary-700">
              I can help you set up hosting and domain registration with reliable providers. I'll guide you through the process and ensure everything is configured correctly. Hosting costs are separate and typically range from â‚¬5-15/month.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm bloom-card">
          <button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFAQ('faq-5')">
            <span class="font-alexandria font-medium text-primary-800">Can I update the website myself?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" id="faq-5-arrow">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div id="faq-5" class="hidden px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-primary-700">
              Absolutely! I build websites that are easy to update. I'll provide training and documentation so you can make content changes, add new photos, and update information without needing technical skills.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  function toggleFAQ(id) {
    const content = document.getElementById(id);
    const arrow = document.getElementById(id + '-arrow');
    
    if (content.classList.contains('hidden')) {
      content.classList.remove('hidden');
      arrow.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
    } else {
      content.classList.add('hidden');
      arrow.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
    }
  }
</script>